  "title": "Data Engineer (Up $6k, Contract, East, Telco industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: East area</strong><br /><strong>Mon – Fri, 9am to 6pm</strong><br /><strong>Immediate - 6 months</strong><br /><strong>Up $6k basic (based on experience and education)</strong></p><p><strong>Duties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Migrate data, tables, and schemas from <strong>Netezza to Snowflake</strong></p></li><li><p>Convert and optimise <strong>ETL/ELT pipelines</strong> for cloud performance</p></li><li><p>Design and enhance <strong>data models and data marts</strong></p></li><li><p>Perform <strong>data validation and testing</strong> to ensure accuracy</p></li><li><p>Document migration processes and data structures</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with analytics and data science teams to support reporting needs<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>3–5 years’ experience in data engineering</p></li><li><p>Strong <strong>SQL</strong>, ETL, and data warehousing skills</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience with <strong>Snowflake</strong> and cloud platforms (AWS)</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in <strong>Python or Scala</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience with legacy-to-cloud data migration<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Interested applicants, please send your resume to aliciasl.lim[at]recruitfirst.co or click \"Apply Now\" below</strong></p><p>Alicia Lim Si Le</p><p>R2197748</p><p>EA License No. 13C6342</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.Thank you</p><p>RecruitFirst is Hiring! You'll be deployed to the above.</p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
